      <title>比特币矿工马拉松计划进行购买以抵消奖励“减半”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/bitcoin-miner-marathon-mara-plans-to-make-purchases-to-offset-reward-halving</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最大的比特币挖矿公司之一马拉松数字控股公司 (Marathon Digital Holdings Inc.) 计划购买更多电力基础设施并插入新机器，以在比特币代码更新将大幅减少矿工收入后保持较低成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/bitcoin-miner-marathon-mara-plans-to-make-purchases-to-offset-reward-halving</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 17:08:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
